---
title: Loaded Pork Fajita Bowl on Mexican Rice with Roasted Veggies and Cheddar Cheese
description: Bold Mexican flavours are both comforting and exciting in this loaded pork fajita bowl! Top fragrant Mexican rice with tender pork, roasted veggies and cheese!
